    "description": "In Stealth Kart, we mix Real-Time Tactics and Fun Racing. Sneak past the policemen's eyes or get into hot pursuits.<br>The green friend has a fast car and needs to get to the goal. One friendly kid might put the enemy into cardboard boxes or hide in one. Another friendly kid has a ramp car, allowing crazy jumps. The third kid has his dad's donut food truck, avoiding suspicion by selling donuts.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Real-Time Tactics meets Racing gameplay: Pick up and play, beat a level in minutes<br></li><li>Later levels are old-school challenging<br></li><li>Four playable characters, all with unique abilities<br></li><li>Local coop option: real-time tactical teamwork<br></li><li>Hide in cardboard boxes, jump over ramps, drive the ramp car, swim, distract policemen with donuts<br></li><li>Cameraderie between a green alien and friendly kids<br></li><li>Vist gramps for a few tips<br></li><li>Longtime motivation: Replay levels with different approaches for medals<br></li><li>Choose your playstyle: Hot pursuits! Or stealthy sneaking. Or making the policemen swim.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838540/extras/29f421f96cb9b97d7c2a35d8100489af.poster.avif?t=1664096599\" width=578 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838540/extras/29f421f96cb9b97d7c2a35d8100489af.webm?t=1664096599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838540/extras/29f421f96cb9b97d7c2a35d8100489af.mp4?t=1664096599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838540/extras/b502b0b9be07f693f7eee78c9c1a7a71.poster.avif?t=1664096599\" width=800 height=448 ><s